    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"letting go\" feels more like just disappearing. it's not like a new beginning, it's just... nothingness. there's no spark left to start something new. it just feels like the world is moving on and i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. do you think it's even possible to feel alive again at this point?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
